<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٢١٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1547">حَفْصُ بْنُ عُمَرَ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4340">عَدِيِّ بْنِ ثَابِتٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/895">الْبَرَاءِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> لِحَسَّانَ: اهْجُهُمْ أَوْ هَاجِهِمْ وَجِبْرِيلُ مَعَكَ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>